{"id":"d4b1ea5708dd532930a85188b45aff6f0a3ed458500c7577e0127a538eb0d100","item_id":"80e5511461:0","text":"Overview（概览）"}
{"id":"5a0822a2c40fc296a5f0f8e844c6363b752b2f83f1852ed513361ae16eb57a3f","item_id":"80e5511461:1","text":"Baking（烘焙）允许用户将图案网络预计算，或将其“烘焙”为 2D 纹理图像或 3D 点云。Baking 有几个优势："}
{"id":"fc15ef339394fdf09db142b7d0d1b48b2a51f03e875c1a0e8bc999743d0f9db9","item_id":"80e5511461:2","text":"通过避免在运行时计算昂贵的图案网络来缩短渲染时间。这种节省可以跨许多帧累积。"}
{"id":"b9cd29dbdf0308d6621e9ee694cd649d49a7a53e990e156d5f53b78259ce2228","item_id":"80e5511461:3","text":"作为着色管线的一部分发布外观开发资产。"}
{"id":"71902d3943dfd58ac5fc8a71ab53912fba41d30ed6bbf2440bf405a82cdc14ad","item_id":"80e5511461:4","text":"无需使用 Pref，即可从参考位置锁定程序化图案信息"}
{"id":"6f21c7bdd5f9d947fdee5cfc6b811c031bfc454110e4401affee40dfdaffd5ee","item_id":"80e5511461:5","text":"在渲染器、实时视口和 3D 打印之间传递资产。"}
{"id":"38281b6432798fa65afad0dd5754a2dd09e31e60717caa1b3289f10ef07643be","item_id":"80e5511461:6","text":"Baking 在 RenderMan 中通过直通图案插件公开，这些插件允许用户从同一场景同时渲染和烘焙。无需大量修改资产或场景，用户即可："}
{"id":"28315267d8e3281557b145a28a28ea482e4924e778daba26c56278f9b9a35fa5","item_id":"80e5511461:7","text":"使用之前已烘焙的结果（如果存在），或者"}
{"id":"6d08fd5618bccc68b13ca32505845d1200914f51a01e481a57b1fa18cc6c270d","item_id":"80e5511461:8","text":"Read（读取）图案网络，而不是读取已烘焙结果。这可能因任何原因发生，但通常是因为已烘焙结果不存在，或用户希望忽略已烘焙结果以便调整图案网络。"}
{"id":"256f39ff106d08d706df993092cb026c8a12ee23f11250b63de7bdc76e53af84","item_id":"80e5511461:9","text":"Baking 本身通过使用 bake hider（烘焙 hider）启用。"}
{"id":"6a547bae367b1b33ec1318d184c51cba86305295861d7c30589ac682754f03e3","item_id":"80e5511461:10","text":"Texture Baking（纹理烘焙）"}
{"id":"91194fe691ba011e8e8d59e0969f17cc7046ce00b43ca61a58fbdd0efad568ea","item_id":"80e5511461:11","text":"2D 烘焙允许用户将图案信号烘焙到纹理图像。用户可以直接烘焙到"}
{"id":"f03ea00b18d9aa9880720aacfb2abc16fe6ae8e4342fd78d93c1c73a4059b349","item_id":"80e5511461:12","text":"txmake"}
{"id":"c66b6305ff99457509f5ae27c2dd661cb08a9bfa7cd9e823c39d3e38aaf2cdfd","item_id":"80e5511461:13","text":"(.tex)、TIFF (.tif) 和 OpenEXR (.exr) 输出。2D 烘焙要求用户提供格式良好的 texture manifold（纹理流形），也就是说，用户已按需求正确创建并布局 UVs。虽然最常见的纹理流形是 ST，但也支持任意流形。也支持 UDIM 等图集输出。"}
{"id":"253cf2e69f5a6ad2855976a6f0b16792be74a0deaee273715cb83799fb2090d0","item_id":"80e5511461:14","text":"RenderMan 提供一个通用纹理烘焙图案："}
{"id":"b4ceaff3b9cf94e655994dafdf1ef23d69440d3a514a31b9d3be8aca65bdbb17","item_id":"80e5511461:15","text":"PxrBakeTexture"}
{"id":"ca80248501e8367be7d8590c51b5b9e2c4ccaf005f91e445265005ae033f9836","item_id":"80e5511461:16","text":"对于重叠的 texture manifold（纹理流形），Baking 行为未定义。"}
{"id":"a268fd121222eeb29d2ef3c71a8345ead43b042b312db99d73f9b3d156efe1c0","item_id":"80e5511461:17","text":"Point Cloud Baking（点云烘焙）"}
{"id":"29ea4dd8850c0d96e0284c130fa3df05d109e6bce86a1c0b8e953f092de18cb6","item_id":"80e5511461:18","text":"RenderMan 提供一个通用点云烘焙图案："}
{"id":"55dae582a8ac16274be0c887a3d38271ee39c70696b3c851ba5b4d8c8e0e57ba","item_id":"80e5511461:19","text":"PxrBakePointCloud"}
{"id":"c780ac97202fe1791a69989660adf131f5785ec031ee39209c1349d125caf32d","item_id":"80e5511461:20","text":"。这可用于生成 Ptex 图像。"}
{"id":"f1f401834f4dee722e2ac523abc827b88491c322b159bdc7c9a013e5529ae2c7","item_id":"80e5511461:21","text":"Blender Setup（Blender 设置）"}
{"id":"9f1fb811f355f95e26dd9a8e94a20fb21a203bd6861172aa7e5a08d98537c7d7","item_id":"80e5511461:22","text":"Baking 可以在 render properties（渲染属性）"}
{"id":"03d3b6aa65a529478e36e2ebebd6c877db149c4f81a8d2280bfc13dca60423fa","item_id":"80e5511461:23","text":"中的 Baking panel（烘焙面板）下设置。"}
{"id":"6a3d4a29a1a80e58d3bee1ffafb9bbc663f2e24802219f8f94a2693f904b0040","item_id":"80e5511461:24","text":"Bake（烘焙）"}
{"id":"77763a37a6d0c0307ef68630cf0d4ca82d9fb9e5e8a33bd0fdd56fdeb071aeb2","item_id":"80e5511461:25","text":"这会启动一个单帧烘焙渲染。如果想处理多帧，或想执行批量渲染，请使用 External Bake Render 按钮（参见"}
{"id":"5bd6cd38918929c15ad99bc4d31245659f7aed7cdbfb6923dc5ce378ced84f96","item_id":"80e5511461:26","text":"Blender 中的批量渲染"}
{"id":"c77d69d93d44e0adf53bed91c3500f1aeaad1cb0b8c1aaf5a2355ed98f7bafbe","item_id":"80e5511461:27","text":"Bake Mode（烘焙模式）"}
{"id":"fc105b4b5f0a2fe37abbb1dd3ab2572b3e1773e7884c1a8ff49bd0abb4ea050f","item_id":"80e5511461:28","text":"在 Pattern（图案）、Illumination（照明）或 All（全部）之间选择。图案模式要求对象的材质着色器网络中某处存在 PxrBakeTexture 或 PxrBakePointCloud；照明模式会将每个 AOV 烘焙为 pointcloud (.ptc) 文件或 2D 纹理文件；全部模式会同时烘焙图案和照明。"}
{"id":"2da25618e04a6740d2ac8e9a231f0d3c143cc0526c076912ec7624670b55ee64","item_id":"80e5511461:29","text":"Baking Illumination Mode（照明烘焙模式）"}
{"id":"d7b543d6f6a27fa82181ce11b482c1936aa2fe1d4fc75b183dca09ffe6dcda54","item_id":"80e5511461:30","text":"烘焙照明时，2D 会写入 2D 纹理，3D 会写入 3D 点云文件（.ptc）。"}
{"id":"77a283d69258c2ae985dc2343725d0af253da0fc1d87626966f7cefe4a3c7469","item_id":"80e5511461:31","text":"Density（密度）"}
{"id":"34cfa9c175d7ffa632500a8ff57014f092d53c7372af2fcf0b30fe908afd262a","item_id":"80e5511461:32","text":"执行 3D 烘焙时，此项决定 point cloud（点云）的密度。数值越低，创建的点云文件越密集。"}
{"id":"d4055fafa3794fa88b1e89e70c167d5a9575067a1442a6d94e9520d65a575378","item_id":"80e5511461:33","text":"Resolution（分辨率）"}
{"id":"a2527851c431225f67f834fec89946a6670d29e62b0031e39f7e16abc409b1c2","item_id":"80e5511461:34","text":"如果是 2D 烘焙，此项决定要写出的 2D 纹理分辨率。"}
{"id":"e994f8afe973d3bd4c36dd558df38a2212d6f6c65e92e8fda0bdeea8f0083985","item_id":"80e5511461:35","text":"Filename Pattern（文件名模式）"}
{"id":"e05bcd9cb0918dd187ebd72d77559b6e6184b6006a08799e432f69eb88b0023c","item_id":"80e5511461:36","text":"执行照明烘焙时，此控制项指定应使用的 filename pattern（文件名模式）。Global 会把所有对象烘焙到一个文件中。Identifier 会为每个对象烘焙一个文件，并用对象名称作为文件名。Filename Attribute 会使用对象在 Baking panel 中 filename attribute（文件名属性）上设置的任何值（参见 object properties（对象属性）"}
{"id":"3750b61b74000e27d09f9c6641e49f01c5cc5c9c59b7b453f89912ec08426be3","item_id":"80e5511461:37","text":"Primvar S/Primvar T"}
{"id":"3c6539ace3aefde757d39774ff178d61856d7727a3d63b356a942211c6ef5965","item_id":"80e5511461:38","text":"对于 2D 烘焙，可以通过设置 RenderMan 应用于 u 和 v 的 primitive variable（图元变量）名称，来使用不同的 UV set（UV 集）。"}
{"id":"e3109eb112b8b5d6dd25efb433f70bf813e165da8c7f3800a0e999d7ee918b11","item_id":"80e5511461:39","text":"Invert T"}
{"id":"131e04ad4651a2d976a0bf41e35839cebcbf9c445919836a2152c8e86a234eca","item_id":"80e5511461:40","text":"RenderMan 是否应反转 T 方向纹理坐标中的值。"}
